<title type="html"><![CDATA[Travelling in the Pursuit of Knowledge-Imām Khaṭib al-Baghdadī [463H]]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=260&amp;p=269#p269"><![CDATA[
<strong><em>Travelling in the Pursuit of Knowledge</em></strong> being a translation <em><strong>Riḥla Fī Ṭalab al-Ḥadīth</strong></em>, which is essentially travelling and enduring patience in seeking knowledge of the sacred sciences and the knowledge of Ḥadīth being a very important one.<br /><br />This is the amazing work of the great Imām of Baghdād who is none other that al-Imām Hāfiẓ Abū Bakr Aḥmad ibn ʾAli ibn Thābit al-Khaṭib al-Baghdādī who died in 463H. This book highlights and explains the great importance and need to pursue knowledge. This book is a must for every student of knowledge who aspires to traverse the blessed path to acquire sacred knowledge.<br /><br />Imām Khaṭib al-Baghdādī is known for his works and his deep insight in the various sciences and disciplines and it is often said about him that he authored a book in every science and branch of Islamic knowledge, this alone shows the importance and great virtue of sciences of Islām<br /><br />This is Dar al-Arqams 5th publication and what a gem it is.<br /><br />THE BOOK IS DUE TO BE PUBLISHED IN 2-4 WEEKS TIME.<br /><br />You may place an order now and reserve and receive it as soon as it arrives    <br /><br />pp.128<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://salafiri.bigcartel.com/product/travelling-in-the-pursuit-of-knowledge-imam-khatib-al-baghdadi-463h">http://salafiri.bigcartel.com/product/t ... hdadi-463h</a><!-- m --><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=32" class="postimage" alt="Rihla-Khatib.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=49">SRI</a> — Sat Sep 03, 2016 11:51 pm</p><hr />
